<concept id="what_this_manual_is_not" xml:lang="en">
    <title>What This Manual Is Not</title>
    <shortdesc>This manual is not a tutorial, and is not a recommended way to learn the ConTeXt
        typesetting system.</shortdesc>
    <conbody>
        <p>Materials for learning <ph conkeyref="definitions/product_name"/> are avaiable through the <xref href="http://www.contextgarden.net" scope="external" format="html">project website</xref>.</p>
        <p>The <ph conkeyref="definitions/product_name"/> Project offers several manuals to help new users get started.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <xref href="http://www.pragma-ade.nl/general/manuals/ma-cb-en.pdf" scope="external" format="pdf"><ph conkeyref="definitions/product_name"/>, an Excurion</xref> is a beginner's manual for the typesetting system.
            </li>
            <li>
                <xref href="http://pmrb.free.fr/contextref.pdf" scope="external" format="pdf">The <ph conkeyref="definitions/product_name"/> Reference Manual</xref> provides coverage for all aspects of the typesetting system.
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p><ph conkeyref="definitions/product_name"/> also ships with many <xref href="https://wiki.contextgarden.net/Manuals" scope="external" format="html">manuals that detail individual parts of the system</xref>.</p>
    </conbody>
